570008,120,1380,2,31,1,206,28,So tato cuto amutra udapādin ti so ahaṃ tato bhavato yonito gatito viññāṇaṭṭhitito sattāvāsato sattanikāyato vā cuto puna amukasmiṃ nāma bhave yoniyā gatiyā viññāṇaṭṭhitiyā sattāvāse sattanikāye vā udapādiṃ. 
570009,120,1380,32,45,1,99,13,Tatrāpāsin ti atha tatrāpi bhave yoniyā gatiyā viññāṇaṭṭhitiyā sattāvāse sattanikāye vā puna ahosiṃ. 
570010,120,1380,46,49,1,27,2,{Evaṃnāmo}tiādi vuttanayameva. 
570011,120,1380,50,88,1,252,27,"Apica yasmā amutrāsin ti idaṃ anupubbena ārohantassa yāvaticchakaṃ( visuddhi.2.410) anussaraṇaṃ, so tato {cuto}ti paṭinivattantassa paccavekkhaṇaṃ, tasmā {idhūpapanno}ti imissā idhūpapattiyā anantaramevassa upapattiṭṭhānaṃ sandhāya amutra udapādin ti idaṃ vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
570012,120,1380,89,101,1,122,12,Tatrāpāsin ti evamādi panassa tatra imissā upapattiyā anantare upapattiṭṭhāne nāmagottādīnaṃ anussaraṇadassanatthaṃ vuttaṃ. 
570013,120,1380,102,119,1,130,16,So tato cuto {idhūpapanno}ti svāhaṃ tato anantarūpapattiṭṭhānato cuto idha amukasmiṃ nāma khattiyakule vā brāhmaṇakule vā nibbattoti. 
