572630,120,1771,23,33,1,89,10,Sappītike dve jhāne samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya jhānasampayuttaṃ pītiṃ khayato vayato sammasati. 
572631,120,1771,34,43,1,83,9,Evaṃ vipassanākkhaṇe jhānasampayuttaṃ pītiṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā cittaṃ āmodeti pamodeti. 
572632,120,1771,44,57,1,83,9,Evaṃ paṭipanno‘‘ abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmi passasissāmīti sikkhatī’’ ti vuccati. 
572633,120,1772,2,50,1,401,42,"Samādahaṃ cittan ti paṭhamajjhānādivasena ārammaṇe cittaṃ samaṃ ādahanto samaṃ ṭhapento, tāni vā pana jhānāni samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya jhānasampayuttaṃ cittaṃ khayato vayato sammasato vipassanākkhaṇe lakkhaṇapaṭivedhena uppajjati khaṇikacittekaggatā, evaṃ uppannāya khaṇikacittekaggatāya vasenapi ārammaṇe cittaṃ samaṃ ādahanto samaṃ ṭhapento‘‘ samādahaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmi passasissāmīti sikkhatī’’ ti vuccati. "
