576768,120,2366,2,30,1,227,25,"‘ ‘ Addasā kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena tena yakkhena āyasmato sāriputtassa sīse pahāraṃ dīyamānaṃ, disvā yena āyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca–"
