576974,120,2404,84,129,1,262,36,"Sāpi dasame māse puttaṃ vijāyitvā navabhājanaṃ āharāpetvā tattha taṃ dārakaṃ nipajjāpetvā taṃ bhājanaṃ pidahitvā upari pupphadāmāni ṭhapetvā‘‘ imaṃ sīsena ukkhipitvā gantvā gaṅgāya vissajjehi,‘ kiṃ idan’ ti ca puṭṭhā‘ ayyāya me balikamman’ ti vadeyyāsī’’ ti dāsiṃ āṇāpesi. "
576975,120,2404,130,133,1,14,3,Sā tathā akāsi. 
576976,120,2404,134,152,1,106,14,Heṭṭhāgaṅgāyapi dve itthiyo nhāyamānā taṃ bhājanaṃ udakena āhariyamānaṃ disvā ekā‘‘ mayhetaṃ bhājanan’’ ti āha. 
576977,120,2404,153,194,1,161,27,"Ekā‘‘ yaṃ etassa anto, taṃ mayhan’’ ti vatvā bhājane sampatte taṃ ādāya thale ṭhapetvā vivaritvā dārakaṃ disvā ekā‘‘ mama bhājanan’’ ti vuttattā‘‘ dārako mameva hotī’’ ti āha. "
576978,120,2404,195,216,1,63,12,"Ekā‘‘ yaṃ bhājanassa anto, taṃ mamā’’ ti vuttattā‘‘ mama dārako’’ ti āha. "
576979,120,2404,217,227,1,89,10,Tā vivadamānā vinicchayaṃ gantvā amaccesu vinicchituṃ asakkontesu rañño santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
576980,120,2404,228,244,1,64,11,"Rājā tāsaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ tvaṃ dārakaṃ gaṇha, tvaṃ bhājanan’’ ti āha. "
576981,120,2404,245,254,1,66,8,"Yāya pana dārako laddho, sā mahākaccāyanattherassa upaṭṭhāyikā hoti. "
576982,120,2404,255,267,1,54,8,Sā taṃ dārakaṃ‘‘ therassa santike pabbājessāmī’’ ti posesi. 
576983,120,2404,268,277,1,79,9,Tassa jātadivase gabbhamalassa dhovitvā anapanītattā kesā jaṭitā hutvā aṭṭhaṃsu. 
576984,120,2404,278,282,1,31,4,Tenassa jaṭiloteva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
576985,120,2405,2,10,1,56,8,Tassa padasā vicaraṇakāle thero taṃ gehaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
576986,120,2405,11,15,1,38,4,Upāsikā theraṃ nisīdāpetvā āhāramadāsi. 
576987,120,2405,16,30,1,54,9,"Thero dārakaṃ disvā‘‘ upāsike, dārako te laddho’’ ti pucchi."
576988,120,2405,31,46,1,63,9,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, imāhaṃ tumhākaṃ santike pabbājessanti posesin’’ ti āha. "
576989,120,2405,47,99,1,274,37,"Thero‘‘ sādhū’’ ti taṃ ādāya gacchanto‘‘ atthi nu kho imassa gihisampattiṃ anubhavituṃ puññakamman’’ ti olokento‘‘ mahāpuñño satto mahāsampattiṃ anubhavissati, daharo eva ca tāva, ñāṇampi tāvassa paripākaṃ na gacchatī’’ ti cintetvā taṃ ādāya takkasilāyaṃ ekassa upaṭṭhākassa gehaṃ agamāsi. "
576990,120,2405,100,117,1,69,11,"So theraṃ vanditvā ṭhito dārakaṃ disvā‘‘ dārako, bhante, laddho’’ ti pucchi."
576991,120,2405,118,134,1,57,9,"‘‘ Āma, upāsaka, pabbajissati, daharo tāva tava santike hotū’’ ti. "
576992,120,2405,135,148,1,53,8,"So‘‘ sādhu, bhante’’ ti taṃ puttaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā paṭijaggi. "
576993,120,2405,149,157,1,55,8,Tassa pana gehe dvādasa vassāni bhaṇḍakaṃ ussannaṃ hoti. 
576994,120,2405,158,184,1,170,22,So gāmantaraṃ gacchanto sabbampi taṃ bhaṇḍakaṃ āpaṇaṃ āharitvā tassa tassa bhaṇḍakassa mūlaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ idañcidañca ettakaṃ nāma dhanaṃ gahetvā dadeyyāsī’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. 
576995,120,2406,2,13,1,107,10,Taṃ divasaṃ nagarapariggāhikā devatā antamaso jīrakamaricamattakenāpi atthike tasseva āpaṇābhimukhe kariṃsu. 
576996,120,2406,14,20,1,57,6,So dvādasa vassāni ussannabhaṇḍakaṃ ekadivaseneva vikkiṇi. 
576997,120,2406,21,39,1,76,12,"Kuṭumbiko āgantvā āpaṇe kiñci adisvā‘‘ sabbaṃ te, tāta, bhaṇḍakaṃ nāsitan’’ ti āha."
576998,120,2406,40,66,1,122,17,"‘‘ Na nāsitaṃ, tāta, sabbaṃ tumhehi vuttanayena vikkiṇitaṃ, idaṃ asukassa mūlaṃ, idaṃ asukassa mūlan’’ ti sabbamūlaṃ tasseva appesi. "
576999,120,2406,67,108,1,204,28,"Kuṭumbiko pasīditvā‘‘ anaggho puriso yattha katthaci jīvituṃ samattho’’ ti attano vayappattaṃ dhītaraṃ tassa datvā‘‘ gehamassa karothā’’ ti purise āṇāpetvā niṭṭhite gehe‘‘ gacchatha tumhe, attano gehe vasathā’’ ti āha. "
577000,120,2406,109,121,1,126,12,Athassa gehapavisanakāle ekena pādena ummāre akkantamatte gehassa pacchimabhāge bhūmiṭṭhāne asītihattho suvaṇṇapabbato uṭṭhahi. 
577001,120,2406,122,134,1,99,12,Rājā kira jaṭilassa gehe bhūmiṃ bhinditvā suvaṇṇapabbato uṭṭhitoti sutvā tassa seṭṭhichattaṃ pesesi. 
577002,120,2406,135,142,1,53,7,So jaṭilaseṭṭhi nāma ahosīti ayamassa puññavato iddhi. 
577003,120,2407,2,20,1,120,12,Meṇḍakassa seṭṭhissa puññavato {iddhī}ti( mahāva.296) meṇḍako nāma vipassimhi bhagavati katādhikāro magadharaṭṭhe bhaddiyanagare seṭṭhi. 
577004,120,2407,21,42,1,204,20,"Tassa kira pacchimagehe aṭṭhakarīsamatte ṭhāne hatthiassausabhappamāṇā suvaṇṇameṇḍakā pathaviṃ bhinditvā piṭṭhiyā piṭṭhiṃ paharamānā uṭṭhahiṃsu, tesaṃ mukhesu pañcavaṇṇānaṃ suttānaṃ geṇḍukā pakkhittā honti. "
577005,120,2407,43,53,1,107,10,Sappitelamadhuphāṇitādīhi ca vatthacchādanahiraññasuvaṇṇādīhi ca atthe sati tesaṃ mukhato geṇḍukaṃ apanenti. 
577006,120,2407,54,61,1,122,7,Ekassapi meṇḍakassa mukhato sakalajambudīpavāsīnaṃ pahonakaṃ sappitelamadhuphāṇitavatthacchādanahiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ nikkhamati. 
577007,120,2407,62,69,1,66,7,Tato paṭṭhāyesa meṇḍakaseṭṭhīti paññāyīti ayamassa puññavato iddhi. 
577008,120,2408,2,28,1,112,11,Ghositassa gahapatissa puññavato {iddhī}ti ghosito( a. ni. aṭṭha.1.1.260-261) nāma paccekasambuddhe katādhikāro sakkaraṭṭhe kosambiyaṃ seṭṭhi. 
577009,120,2408,29,37,1,73,8,So kira devalokato cavitvā kosambiyaṃ nagarasobhiniyā kucchismiṃ nibbatti. 
577010,120,2408,38,45,1,58,7,Sā taṃ vijātadivase suppe sayāpetvā saṅkārakūṭe chaḍḍāpesi. 
577011,120,2408,46,50,1,41,4,Dārakaṃ kākasunakhā parivāretvā nisīdiṃsu. 
577012,120,2408,51,67,1,77,12,Eko puriso taṃ disvāva puttasaññaṃ paṭilabhitvā‘‘ putto me laddho’’ ti gehaṃ nesi. 
577013,120,2408,68,104,1,163,21,"Tadā kosambikaseṭṭhi purohitaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ, ācariya, ajja te tithikaraṇanakkhattādayo olokitā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ āma, mahāseṭṭhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ janapadassa kiṃ bhavissatī’’ ti pucchi."
577014,120,2408,105,117,1,61,8,‘‘ Imasmiṃ nagare ajja jātadārako jeṭṭhaseṭṭhi bhavissatī’’ ti āha. 
577015,120,2408,118,145,1,103,18,"Tadā seṭṭhino bhariyā garugabbhā hoti, tasmā so sīghaṃ gehaṃ pesesi‘‘ gaccha, jānāhi naṃ vijātā vā, na vā’’ ti."
577016,120,2408,146,177,1,145,22,"‘‘ Na vijātā’’ ti sutvā gehaṃ gantvā kāḷiṃ nāma dāsiṃ pakkositvā sahassaṃ datvā‘‘ gaccha, imasmiṃ nagare upadhāretvā ajja jātadārakaṃ gaṇhitvā ehī’’ ti āha. "
577017,120,2408,178,194,1,106,16,Sā upadhārentī taṃ gehaṃ gantvā taṃ dārakaṃ taṃ divasaṃ jātaṃ ñatvā sahassaṃ datvā ānetvā seṭṭhino dassesi. 
577018,120,2408,195,210,1,91,12,"Seṭṭhi‘‘ sace me dhītā jāyissati, tāya naṃ saddhiṃ nivāsetvā seṭṭhiṭṭhānassa sāmikaṃ karissāmi. "
577019,120,2408,211,224,1,67,10,"Sace putto jāyissati, ghātessāmi nan’’ ti cintetvā taṃ gehe vaḍḍhāpesi. "
577020,120,2409,2,7,1,45,5,Athassa bhariyā katipāhaccayena puttaṃ vijāyi. 
577021,120,2409,8,17,1,56,7,Seṭṭhi‘‘ imasmiṃ asati mama putto seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ labhissati. 
577022,120,2409,18,53,1,205,26,"Idāneva naṃ māretuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti kāḷiṃ āmantetvā‘‘ gaccha je, vajato gunnaṃ nikkhamanavelāya vajadvāramajjhe imaṃ tiriyaṃ nipajjāpehi, gāviyo naṃ madditvā māressanti, madditāmadditabhāvaṃ panassa ñatvā ehī’’ ti āha. "
577023,120,2409,54,62,1,68,8,Sā gantvā gopālakena vajadvāre vivaṭamatteyeva taṃ tathā nipajjāpesi. 
577024,120,2409,63,78,1,144,15,Gogaṇajeṭṭhako usabho aññasmiṃ kāle sabbapacchā nikkhamantopi taṃdivasaṃ sabbapaṭhamaṃ nikkhamitvā dārakaṃ catunnaṃ pādānaṃ antare katvā aṭṭhāsi. 
577025,120,2409,79,86,1,60,7,Anekasatā gāvo usabhassa dve passāni ghaṃsantiyo nikkhamiṃsu. 
577026,120,2409,87,130,1,237,33,"Gopālakopi‘‘ ayaṃ usabho pubbe sabbapacchā nikkhamati, ajja pana paṭhamaṃ nikkhamitvā dvāramajjhe niccalova ṭhito, kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti cintetvā gantvā tassa heṭṭhā nipannaṃ dārakaṃ disvā puttasinehaṃ paṭilabhitvā‘‘ putto me laddho’’ ti gehaṃ nesi. "
577027,120,2410,2,25,1,117,18,"Kāḷī gantvā seṭṭhinā pucchitā tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ gaccha, naṃ puna imaṃ sahassaṃ datvā ānehī’’ ti vuttā puna ānetvā adāsi. "
577028,120,2410,26,30,1,19,4,Atha naṃ seṭṭhi āha–
577029,120,2410,31,66,1,203,25,"‘‘ amma kāḷi, imasmiṃ nagare pañcasakaṭasatāni paccūsakāle uṭṭhāya vāṇijjāya gacchanti, tvaṃ imaṃ netvā cakkamagge nipajjāpehi, goṇā vā naṃ maddissanti, cakkaṃ vā chindissati, pavattiñcassa ñatvā āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti. "
577030,120,2410,67,71,1,32,4,Sā gantvā cakkamagge nipajjāpesi. 
577031,120,2410,72,75,1,29,3,Sākaṭikajeṭṭhako purato ahosi. 
577032,120,2410,76,90,1,99,13,"Athassa goṇā taṃ ṭhānaṃ patvā dhuraṃ chaḍḍesuṃ, punappunaṃ āropetvā pājiyamānāpi purato na gacchiṃsu. "
577033,120,2410,91,98,1,53,7,Evaṃ tassa tehi saddhiṃ vāyamantasseva aruṇaṃ uṭṭhahi. 
577034,120,2410,99,135,1,137,23,So‘‘ kiṃ nāma goṇā kariṃsū’’ ti maggaṃ olokento dārakaṃ disvā‘‘ bhāriyaṃ vata kamman’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ putto me laddho’’ ti tuṭṭhamānaso taṃ gehaṃ nesi. 
