577045,120,2412,25,29,1,18,4,Aya naṃ seṭṭhi āha–
577046,120,2412,30,54,1,172,17,"‘‘ amma, imaṃ ādāya corapapātapabbataṃ abhiruhitvā papāte khipa, pabbatakucchiyaṃ paṭihaññamāno khaṇḍākhaṇḍiko hutvā bhūmiyaṃ patissati, matāmatabhāvañcassa ñatvā āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti. "
577047,120,2412,55,62,1,47,7,Sā taṃ tathā netvā pabbatamatthake ṭhatvā khipi. 
577048,120,2412,63,77,1,123,13,"Taṃ kho pana pabbatakucchiṃ nissāya mahāveḷugumbo pabbatānusāreneva vaḍḍhi, tassa matthakaṃ ghanajāto jiñjukagumbo avatthari. "
577049,120,2412,78,84,1,38,6,Dārako patanto kojave viya tasmiṃ pati. 
