577055,120,2413,2,7,1,49,5,Seṭṭhino idañcidañca karontasseva dārako vaḍḍhito. 
577056,120,2413,8,13,1,48,5,Mahāghosavacanattā cassa ghositoteva nāmaṃ ahosi. 
577057,120,2413,14,27,1,67,10,"So seṭṭhino akkhimhi kaṇṭako viya khāyi, ujukaṃ oloketumpi na visahi. "
577058,120,2413,28,66,1,181,26,Athassa maraṇūpāyaṃ cintento attano kumbhakārassa santikaṃ gantvā tassa‘‘ kadā āvāpaṃ ālimpessasī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ sve’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi idaṃ sahassaṃ gaṇhitvā mamekaṃ kammaṃ karohī’’ ti āha.
577059,120,2413,67,74,1,11,3,‘‘ Kiṃ sāmī’’ ti?
577060,120,2413,75,99,1,161,20,"‘‘ Eko me avajātaputto atthi, taṃ tava santikaṃ pesissāmi, atha naṃ gabbhaṃ pavesetvā tiṇhāya vāsiyā khaṇḍākhaṇḍikaṃ chinditvā cāṭiyaṃ pakkhipitvā āvāpe paveseyyāsīti. "
577061,120,2413,100,114,1,86,11,"Idaṃ te sahassaṃ saccakārasadisaṃ, uttariṃ pana te kattabbayuttakaṃ pacchā karissāmī’’ ti. "
577062,120,2413,115,123,1,31,4,Kumbhakāro‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
577063,120,2414,2,39,1,183,27,"Seṭṭhi punadivase ghositaṃ pakkositvā‘‘ hiyyo mayā kumbhakāro ekaṃ kammaṃ āṇatto, ehi , tvaṃ tāta, tassa santikaṃ gantvā evaṃ vadehi‘ hiyyo kira me pitarā āṇattaṃ kammaṃ nipphādehī’’’ ti pahiṇi. "
577064,120,2414,40,48,1,19,4,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti agamāsi. 
577065,120,2414,49,100,1,265,37,"Taṃ tattha gacchantaṃ itaro seṭṭhino putto dārakehi saddhiṃ guḷakakīḷaṃ kīḷanto disvā pakkositvā‘‘ kuhiṃ gacchasī’’ ti pucchitvā pitu sāsanaṃ gahetvā‘‘ kumbhakārassa santikan’’ ti vutte‘‘ ahaṃ tattha gamissāmi, ime maṃ dārakā bahulakkhaṃ jiniṃsu, taṃ me paṭijinitvā dehī’’ ti āha."
577066,120,2414,101,109,1,20,4,‘‘ Ahaṃ pitu bhāyāmī’’ ti.
577067,120,2414,110,124,1,46,8,"‘‘ Mā bhāyi, bhātika, ahaṃ taṃ sāsanaṃ harissāmī’’ ti."
577068,120,2414,125,139,1,59,9,"‘‘ Bahūhi jito yāvāhaṃ āgacchāmi, tāva me lakkhaṃ paṭijināhī’’ ti. "
577069,120,2414,140,149,1,55,8,"Ghosito kira guḷakakīḷāyaṃ cheko, tena naṃ evaṃ nibandhi. "
577070,120,2414,150,175,1,110,18,"Sopi taṃ‘‘ tena hi gantvā kumbhakāraṃ vadehi‘ pitarā kira me hiyyo ekaṃ kammaṃ āṇattaṃ, taṃ nipphādehī’’’ ti uyyojesi. "
577071,120,2414,176,182,1,36,6,So tassa santikaṃ gantvā tathā avaca. 
577072,120,2414,183,191,1,62,8,Atha naṃ kumbhakāro seṭṭhinā vuttaniyāmena māretvā āvāpe khipi. 
