577074,120,2414,216,249,1,166,23,"Seṭṭhi‘‘ dhī dhī’’ ti mahāviravaṃ viravitvā sakalasarīre pakkuthitalohito viya hutvā‘‘ ambho kumbhakāra, mā nāsayi, mā nāsayī’’ ti bāhā paggayha kandanto tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. "
577075,120,2414,250,269,1,83,13,"Kumbhakāro taṃ tathā āgacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ sāmi, mā saddaṃ kari, kammaṃ nipphannan’’ ti āha. "
577076,120,2414,270,280,1,85,10,So pabbatena viya mahantena sokena avatthaṭo hutvā anappakaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedesi. 
